snippet.title: YouTube
snippet.description: Welcome to YouTube's Spotlight channel, your daily go-to for discovering what's new and trending around the world. From music to culture to Internet phenomena, find those gotta-watch videos from across YouTube, all in one place.

snippet.title: YouTube Creators
snippet.description:
Welcome to the YouTube Creators Channel - formerly known as The Creator Academy. This new channel will be your go-to destination for all things “Creator”, with new content each week including education and inspiration from YouTube experts, and fellow creators. Subscribe and hit the bell to see a new video each Tuesday!

Be sure to also check out the Creator Academy site in the links below. You’ll continue to find the best courses and lessons on a wide variety of topics.
